{"tid":1786660,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警謊是二奶嗎？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-12-17T09:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T11:07:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8953ba2e679dcd373138785d86e5097254dc450c","tid":1786660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191217/20826265/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826265%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=d0812cf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826265%2F&h=008cb3d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191217/20826265/</a><br />\n<br />\n警謊是二奶嗎？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191217/large/1576486280_9bd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576486280_9bd5.jpg&h=8463b7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眾三色台藝人日前去警察總部打氣送暖，與警謊高層及發言人歡樂相聚的相片一放上網，就有出席的藝人（完全不知其姓甚名誰拍過甚麼作品）急急留言：「唔出鏡㗎害死人喇！」。這就奇了，既然滿腔熱情去撐警，當然是因為喜歡警察，認為警察做得對，所以義無反顧去支持。如果相信自己做的事是對的，又有甚麼不見得光？即使千夫所指，又怕甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n私底下去撐警，撐了，卻不敢被人知道。這是甚麼行為？像極了在外包二奶的偷情男，私底下再肉麻的情話也說得出口，卻永遠不敢把二奶帶到公眾場合，朋友問起，一臉地不屑，「怎麼可能？我怎麼會跟那種女人在一起？我是眼光那麼差、要求那麼低的人嗎？」三色台二打六眼中的警謊，像二奶一樣不能見光嗎？一見光，不是警謊亡，而是二打六死。<br />\n<br />\n做警察做到這種地步，實在很侮辱，來了一大堆人，說了一大堆打氣的話，看起來笑容也很熱情，誰知一轉身就不認人。羞於承認撐警。<br />\n<br />\n做藝人做到這種地步，難怪被人叫偽人，工作時穿上戲服是角色扮演，原來不工作的時候也不能做自己。做的是自己都覺得羞於被人知道的事。藝術工作尤重自我及心靈的自由，一個人若無自我，無自由的靈魂，一輩子都不可能成為出色的演員，難怪這批人只能是二打六。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"c343ce76e83dd6ae7e3315341ecf2345d37960aa","tid":1786660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8EhU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8EhU3.jpg&h=c3f3defe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7b904b25a134304ea8f36502d7dce7b02ffab45","tid":1786660,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"人唔要面就天下無敵<br />\n佢地而家話警察係啱嘅，自己歸邊呢條路"},{"pid":"385203a2ef8fb575d7105e9f67abb236a0ed2d58","tid":1786660,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc3ceab37c882e16f034c4f44f6332fcbdf5b1d4","tid":1786660,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"講定先<br />\n示威者及其支持者唔想表露身份原因係怕俾掌權者清算"},{"pid":"08971c7df12ae0d9264023fbc1a4826c9779a63b","tid":1786660,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"睇班黑警毅進狗都係啦，個個蒙面，因為班狗知自己唔見得光，做嘅事唔見得光，同埋已成過街老鼠，試下唔蒙面? 第二日俾人埋左單啦"},{"pid":"82035b480a53e4f5c12ee9a2dd355a7a498ff204","tid":1786660,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"抽晒兩邊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef10778ea7fb2ff93a8fb9147202a50d6ccbd5d","tid":1786660,"uid":270281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c